{
  "texts": [
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first paper to use this approach for open intent discovery in Vietnamese.",
    "The results are evaluated on three datasets: Bank-inf77_eng, Banking77_vni, and HCMUT_FAQ_vni.",
    "Additionally, we perform preliminary experiments on discovering the relationships between intents and other entities to build a KG for the education domain.",
    "We also conduct some experiments on applying the KG to LLM.",
    "A APPENDIX A.1 E-OED Framework AnalysisThis appendix provides further details on the implementation of the E-OED framework."
  ]
}